{"content_excerpt":"# W0 вЂ” Residual da W5 da mega-spec (per-spec-event-log + db redesign + dashboard)\n\n## Contexto\n\nA `2026-05-24-mustard-unification` (encerrada nesta sessГЈo) tinha W5 em execuГ§ГЈo com 8 tarefas. T5.1 (EventSink NDJSON + blob spill) e parte de T5.7 (purge `src-tauri/`) foram entregues por commits recentes. O restante migra para esta wave.\n\n## Tarefas pendentes (origem em T5.X da mega-spec)\n\n- [ ] **T0.1 (era T5.2)** вЂ” Core reader NDJSON. `packages/core/src/projection/timeline.rs` lГЄ NDJSON. `model/view/timeline.rs` com shape novo (`input`, `output`, `tokens_in`, `tokens_out`, `duration_ms`, `parent_id`). `mustard-rt run rebuild-specs` consome NDJSON.\n- [ ] **T0.2 (era T5.3)** вЂ” Dashboard timeline claude-devtools-style. Rewrite `SpecTimelineTab` + `PipelineTimeline` вЂ” lista flat de tool calls; expand revela Input/Output renderizados por tool (Bash/Read/Edit/Glob/Grep/Task recursivo via `parent_id`). Live tail via `notify-rs` no `src-tauri`. Re-render `<16ms` em wave com 500+ eventos.\n- [ ] **T0.3 (era T5.4)** вЂ” Sessions table + sidebar. Tabela `sessions` em `mustard.db` + diretГіrio `.claude/.session/{slug}/events/`. Rota `Sessions.tsx` com sidebar.\n- [ ] **T0.4 (era T5.5)** вЂ” `mustard-rt run spec-clear`. Flags `--dry-run` (default), `--apply`, `--all`, `--name`, `--age-days` (default 15). Algoritmo: glob spec в†’ parse meta.json в†’ filtra Close+Done в†’ mtime mais recente em events/ в†’ cutoff.\n- [ ] **T0.5 (era T5.6)** вЂ” Schema `mustard.db` reescrito do zero. Drop `events`/`events_fts`/`knowledge` legacy/`metrics_projection`. CREATE direto de `pipeline_events`, `sessions`, `knowledge_patterns`, `memory_decisions`, `memory_lessons` (+FTS5), DDL de `agent_memory`+`memory_feedback` (lГіgica em W7). ГЌndices auditados via `EXPLAIN QUERY PLAN`. `VACUUM` final + `PRAGMA optimize` no open.\n- [ ] **T0.6 (era T5.7 residual)** вЂ” Remover componente de grafo interno do dashboard. Remover dep forГ§a-grafo (`react-force-graph`, `d3-force`, `vis-network`) de `apps/dashboard/package.json`. Wikilinks `[[X]]` via `obsidian://open?vault=вЂ¦&file=вЂ¦` ou `shell.open`. Lista virtualizada (`react-virtuoso` ou `@tanstack/react-virtual`). PГЎgina `/specs` `<200ms` para 100 specs.\n- [ ] **T0.7 (era T5.8)** вЂ” Economy events from event-log. EventSink emite `pipeline.economy.event.written { duration_ns, bytes_written, spilled_to_blob }`. VisГ­vel em `/economia` (W11).\n\n## CritГ©rios de AceitaГ§ГЈo\n\n- [ ] **AC-W0.1** вЂ” Tabela `events` dropada do schema. Command: `rtk node -e \"const t=require('fs').readFileSync('packages/core/src/store/sqlite_schema.sql','utf8');if(/CREATE TABLE events\\\\b/.test(t))process.exit(1)\"`\n- [ ] **AC-W0.2** вЂ” `pipeline_events` e `sessions` existem. Command: `rtk node -e \"const t=require('fs').readFileSync('packages/core/src/store/sqlite_schema.sql','utf8');for(const k of ['CREATE TABLE pipeline_events','CREATE TABLE sessions']){if(!t.includes(k))process.exit(1)}\"`\n- [ ] **AC-W0.3** вЂ” `package.json` dashboard sem forГ§a-grafo. Command: `rtk node -e \"const j=JSON.parse(require('fs').readFileSync('apps/dashboard/package.json','utf8'));for(const k of ['react-force-graph','react-force-graph-2d','d3-force','vis-network']){if(j.dependencies?.[k]||j.devDependencies?.[k])process.exit(1)}\"`\n- [ ] **AC-W0.4** вЂ” `mustard-rt run spec-clear --help` lista flags. Command: `rtk mustard-rt run spec-clear --help`\n- [ ] **AC-W0.5** вЂ” Wikilinks no dashboard usam `obsidian://`. Command: validado por inspeГ§ГЈo.\n\n## Limites\n\n`packages/core/src/store/*`, `packages/core/src/projection/timeline.rs`, `packages/core/src/model/view/timeline.rs`, `apps/rt/src/run/spec_clear.rs` (novo), `apps/rt/src/run/rebuild_specs.rs`, `apps/dashboard/src/components/{SpecTimelineTab,PipelineTimeline,Sessions}.tsx`, `apps/dashboard/src/pages/Specs.tsx`, `apps/dashboard/src-tauri/src/main.rs`, `apps/dashboard/package.json`.\n\nOUT: tudo fora. NГѓO mexer em event_writer_ndjson.rs (T5.1 entregue).\n\n## Role\n\nmixed (rt + dashboard + core)\n","file_path":"C:\\Atiz\\mustard\\.claude\\spec\\2026-05-25-mustard-deep-refactor\\wave-0-mixed\\spec.md","tool":"Read","tool_use_id":"toolu_01KfEj4r5XLowRgt35z23PW8"}